  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wouldn't everyone want to have a giant laser battle cat to overcome life's challenges with a devastating beam?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Kittens!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers 5 kittens, each with different stats and appearances. Unlock them by completing levels and give them names. Feed them radioactive milk to make them bigger and stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conquer Five Continents!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cat is equipped with a vest—build a laser mechanism on it. Generate power, store it in batteries, and fire away. Use rotating and sliding parts to reach all enemies. Defeat European pigeons, African snakes, and Australian spiders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take Care of Your Home!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add extra furniture, buy pots, plant valerian and catnip. Water the plants, then prepare potions for your cat. Purchase additional workshop equipment to unlock more components for the laser mechanism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel and destroy!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wouldn't everyone want to have a giant laser battle cat to overcome life's challenges with a devastating beam?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/15d7c6bf03d556aebad397ce3a38fd5f.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Kittens!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game offers 5 kittens, each with different stats and appearances. Unlock them by completing levels and give them names. Feed them radioactive milk to make them bigger and stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/f5e7dec54900d4b0235bab4f0c195ff2.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conquer Five Continents!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cat is equipped with a vest—build a laser mechanism on it. Generate power, store it in batteries, and fire away. Use rotating and sliding parts to reach all enemies. Defeat European pigeons, African snakes, and Australian spiders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.poster.avif?t=1771016281\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.webm?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098920/extras/8b543337ed39c8f9e93af13bd38bc740.mp4?t=1771016281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take Care of Your Home!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add extra furniture, buy pots, plant valerian and catnip. Water the plants, then prepare potions for your cat. Purchase additional workshop equipment to unlock more components for the laser mechanism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel and destroy!</p>",
